# calsedファイル
cat << FIN > $tmp-calsed_data
###USERID###       ${USERID}      
###USERNAME###     ${USERNAME}
###SHISETSUID### ${SHISETSUID}
###SHISETSUNAME### ${SHISETSUNAME}
